description:
125+ photographies. 3 videos. Simple game. Czech super beauty Verunka.

Playful Verunka HD brings the Czech super beauty Verunka exclusively to your
TouchPad. Follow Verunka's commands and desires in an interactive photo mode to unlock two
bonus backstage videos or browse the gallery with all the photographies - Verunka at
the beach, in a hotel room, in a swimming pool and much more...  at your fingertips.

Exhibition mode. Slideshow. Every photo is edited as wallpaper for TouchPad!

Disclaimer: application  may occasionally contain sexual/suggestive material, sexually charged dialogue and self-censored nudity.
